 stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">错误修复</p>\n<p><ul>\n<li>只有一个标签的物品导致致命错误 (7478780)</li>\n<li>代码高亮在刷新后没有高亮显示 (8b77aa2)</li>\n<li>Prism 高亮在重新加载时不渲染 (aa2328e)</li>\n<li>标签在手机端中溢出 (cd9bae9)</li>\n<li>Waline 不同的日期格式导致格式错误 (22477f2)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>特性</p>\n<ul>\n<li>添加好友链接功能 (a4ae01a)</li>\n<li>添加了所有页面的页面和评论的统计 (支持 waline, valine, twikoo)(d107853)</li>\n<li>增加站点运行时长和站点PV (2d15ac6)</li>\n<li>增加valine, twikoo和valine 的文章浏览统计 (517e9d0)<br>&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"hexo-plugin-aurora-v1-3-1-2023-08-04\"><a href=\"#hexo-plugin-aurora-v1-3-1-2023-08-04\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo-plugin-aurora v1.3.1 (2023-08-04)\"></a>hexo-plugin-aurora v1.3.1 (2023-08-04)</h3><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">更新了 hexo-plugin-aurora v1.3.1</p>\n<ul>\n<li>添加了 site.language 配置缺失的提示</li>\n<li>主题配置里面不需要有所有评论插件配置了（之前所有配置不用也要加上，不然会报错）</li>\n<li>主题和生成器版本改为先从 node_modules 中读取，没有就找 themes 文件夹（这样就可以把源码拉到 thems 中自定义了，也不会出现生成器报错了）<br>&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"2-1-0-2023-08-02\"><a href=\"#2-1-0-2023-08-02\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1.0 (2023-08-02)\"></a>2.1.0 (2023-08-02)</h3><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">深夜主题更新版本 2.1.0</p>\n<p><ul>\n<li>添加最近评论的空显示（c4dde9b）</li>\n<li>添加waline评论插件（6f34372）</li>\n<li>插件：添加twikoo评论插件支持（39ccaf8）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>hexo-plugin-aurora 版本 1.3.0</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>修复了 tags 是空时生成器报错问题</li>\n</ul>\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"2-0-1-2023-07-28\"><a href=\"#2-0-1-2023-07-28\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.0.1 (2023-07-28)\"></a>2.0.1 (2023-07-28)</h3><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">版本 2.0.1 发布修复以下问题：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>备案图片导致报错</li>\n<li>文章链接太长导致超出容器<br>&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>\n\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"2-0-0-2023-07-25\"><a href=\"#2-0-0-2023-07-25\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.0.0 (2023-07-25)\"></a>2.0.0 (2023-07-25)</h3><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">Bug修复</p>\n<p><ul>\n<li>代码剪贴板复制按钮样式 (05450c5)</li>\n<li>错误的最近评论 gavatar url 与valine #225 (bfcf168)</li>\n<li>主要作者无法在主页加载 (667e1df)</li>\n<li>移动视图无法获取作者数据 (2e4dOcd)</li>\n<li>正确的设置不会隐藏最近的评论 (91358ad)</li>\n<li>最近的评论总是显示 (0976e5c)</li>\n<li>删除qod，因为它的评级限制为每天5次调用 (75e99da)</li>\n<li>Post (1c58e55) 的 typescript输入问题</li>\n<li>对默认图像使用新导入而不是require (6d1b078)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>特征</p>\n<ul>\n<li>vite&#x2F;dependencies:更新为Vite和所有依赖项 (162df85)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>重大变化</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>vite&#x2F;dependencies:更改为Vite并更新了所有依赖项</li>\n</ul>\n</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"博客的特殊情况\"><a href=\"#博客的特殊情况\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"博客的特殊情况\"></a>博客的特殊情况</h2><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p>如果你像我一样，重装了系统，又保留了整个博客的文件，但是gitbash无法启动</p>\n<p>不必重新安装，可以在gitbash 输入：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>即可</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"杂七杂八的BUG\"><a href=\"#杂七杂八的BUG\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"杂七杂八的BUG\"></a>杂七杂八的BUG</h2><h3 id=\"BUG1-自定义页面跳转404问题\"><a href=\"#BUG1-自定义页面跳转404问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"BUG1 自定义页面跳转404问题\"></a>BUG1 自定义页面跳转404问题</h3><p>网友们给出了解决方案</p>\n<p> <a href=\"https://github.com/auroral-ui/hexo-theme-aurora/issues/185\">在查看文章页面时，一旦刷新，就显示404 issues #185</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"BUG2-预览文字溢出盒子\"><a href=\"#BUG2-预览文字溢出盒子\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"BUG2 预览文字溢出盒子\"></a>BUG2 预览文字溢出盒子</h3><div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">某网友说</p>\n<p>本博客文章底部，评论区附近的“上&#x2F;下一篇文章”处，预览文字会导致盒子高度不一样，可以在文章的md文件开头，通过 <strong>控制预览文字长度</strong> 的 <strong>preview</strong> 来解决，举例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight md\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">preview: 120 #控制预览文字长度</span><br><span class=\"line\">abstracts: &quot;分享....&quot; #自定义预览文字</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>但我个人觉得这个BUG影响不大，可改可不改</p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"BUG3-音乐盒子有问题\"><a href=\"#BUG3-音乐盒子有问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"BUG3 音乐盒子有问题\"></a>BUG3 音乐盒子有问题</h3><p>网友反应，MetingJS 和 APlayerJS 构建的音乐播放器偶尔不行，博主目前也没也想到解决办法，欢迎大佬提供支持。</p>\n<h3 id=\"BUG4-端口占用\"><a href=\"#BUG4-端口占用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"BUG4 端口占用\"></a>BUG4 端口占用</h3><details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>如图所示：</summary>\n<p><img src=\"/../img/Bug/bug-3.png\" alt=\"bug-3\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../img/Bug/bug-4.png\" alt=\"bug-4\"></p>\n\n</details>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>一般常见原因为，同时使用了该端口</p>\n<p><del>比如像博主再VSCode打开端口后，又在Git Bash Here打开</del></p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"BUG5-多个主题（冲突）\"><a href=\"#BUG5-多个主题（冲突）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"BUG5 多个主题（冲突）\"></a>BUG5 多个主题（冲突）</h3><details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>如图所示：</summary>\n<p><p><img src=\"/